CONTEXT(heading_40, 'takes a ballot paper from a polling place without authority,')
heading_36 = heading_30 + ">>is guilty of an offence and is liable to imprisonment for 12 months and a fine of $12 000.; [Section 103 inserted No. 70 of 2004 s. 10.]; [Section 103 inserted No. 70 of 2004 s. 10.]; [Section 103 inserted No. 70 of 2004 s. 10.]; [Section 103 inserted No. 70 of 2004 s. 10.]; [Section 103 inserted No. 70 of 2004 s. 10.]; [Section 103 inserted No. 70 of 2004 s. 10.]; [Section 103 inserted No. 70 of 2004 s. 10.]; [Section 103 inserted No. 70 of 2004 s. 10.]"
