heading_16 = heading_15 + ">>298. Suffocation and strangulation"
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>A person commits a crime if the person unlawfully impedes another persons normal breathing, blood circulation, or both, by manually, or by using any other aid "
heading_18 = heading_17 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'blocking (completely or partially) another persons nose, mouth, or both or')
heading_19 = heading_17 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'applying pressure on, or to, another persons neck.')
heading_18 = heading_16 + ">>content2"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'Alternative offence s. 313.')
heading_16 = heading_11 + ">>Penalty"
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_17, 'if the offence is committed in circumstances of aggravation, imprisonment for 7 years or')
heading_18 = heading_16 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'in any other case, imprisonment for 5 years.')
heading_17 = heading_11 + ">>Summary conviction penalty"
heading_18 = heading_17 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_18, 'in a case to which the Penalty paragraph (a) applies, imprisonment for 3 years and a fine of $36 000 or')
heading_19 = heading_17 + ">>(b) in a case to which the Penalty paragraph (b) applies, imprisonment for 2 years and a fine of $24 000."
heading_20 = heading_19 + ">>299. Terms used in relation to s. 300 (persistent family violence)"
heading_21 = heading_20 + ">>(1) In this section and section 300 "
heading_22 = heading_21 + ">>designated family relationship means a relationship between 2 persons "
heading_23 = heading_22 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_23, 'who are, or were, married to each other or')
heading_24 = heading_22 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_24, 'who are, or were, in a de facto relationship with each other or')
heading_25 = heading_22 + ">>c"
CONTEXT(heading_25, 'who have, or had, an intimate personal relationship with each other')
heading_23 = heading_21 + ">>prescribed offence means "
heading_24 = heading_23 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_24, 'an offence against section 221BD, 298, 301, 304(1), 313, 317, 317A, 323, 324, 338B, 338C, 338E or 444(1)(b), or an attempt to commit such an offence or')
heading_25 = heading_23 + ">>(b) an offence against the"
CONTEXT(heading_25, 'Restraining Orders Act 1997 section 61(1) or (1A).')
heading_22 = heading_20 + ">>(2) For the purposes of this section, an intimate personal relationship exists between 2 persons (including persons of the same sex) if "
heading_23 = heading_22 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_23, 'the persons are engaged to be married to each other, including a betrothal under cultural or religious tradition or')
heading_24 = heading_22 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_24, 'the persons date each other, or have a romantic involvement with each other, whether or not a sexual relationship is involved.')
heading_23 = heading_20 + ">>(3) In deciding whether an intimate personal relationship exists under subsection (2)(b), the following may be taken into account "
heading_24 = heading_23 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_24, 'the circumstances of the relationship, including, for example, the level of trust and commitment')
heading_25 = heading_23 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_25, 'the length of time the relationship has existed')
heading_26 = heading_23 + ">>c"
CONTEXT(heading_26, 'the frequency of contact between the persons')
heading_27 = heading_23 + ">>d"
CONTEXT(heading_27, 'the level of intimacy between the persons.')
heading_24 = heading_20 + ">>(4) For the purposes of this section and section 300, a person does an act of family violence if "
heading_25 = heading_24 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_25, 'the person does an act that would constitute a prescribed offence in relation to another person with whom the person is in a designated family relationship and')
heading_26 = heading_24 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_26, 'the person is not a child at the time of doing the act.')
heading_25 = heading_20 + ">>(5)"
CONTEXT(heading_25, 'For the purposes of this section and section 300, a person persistently engages in family violence if the person does an act of family violence on 3 or more occasions each of which is on a different day over a period not exceeding 10 years against the same person.')
heading_26 = heading_20 + ">>(6) For the purposes of subsection (5), the acts of family violence "
heading_27 = heading_26 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_27, 'need not all constitute the same prescribed offence and')
heading_28 = heading_26 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_28, 'need not all have occurred in this State as long as at least 1 of them did.')
heading_27 = heading_20 + ">>(7)"
CONTEXT(heading_27, 'However, in relation to an act that constitutes a simple offence, an act cannot be an act of family violence if the date at the end of the period during which it is alleged that the acts of family violence occurred for the purposes of this section is outside the period during which it would be possible to charge the accused person with that offence.')
heading_21 = heading_19 + ">>300. Persistent family violence"
heading_22 = heading_21 + ">>(1) A person commits a crime if the person persistently engages in family violence."
CONTEXT(heading_22, 'Penalty for this subsection imprisonment for 14 years.')
heading_23 = heading_21 + ">>(2) A charge of an offence under subsection (1) "
heading_24 = heading_23 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_24, 'must specify the period during which it is alleged that the acts of family violence occurred and')
heading_25 = heading_23 + ">>b"
