heading_31 = heading_27 + ">>(d) a report of family violence, in the approved form, completed by a person who has worked with the tenant and is 1 of the following "
heading_32 = heading_31 + ">>(i) a person registered under the; Health Practitioner Regulation National Law (Western Australia) in the medical profession"
