CONTEXT(heading_44, 'The payment of an amount under section 29(4)(b) must be made as soon as practicable, and in any event within 14 days, after the persons receipt of the bond.')
heading_45 = heading_43 + ">>(2) The payment may be made either directly, including by electronic means, or by lodging the amount with an authorised agent of the bond administrator."
